#summary Overview of Timer control registers per PIC

----

= Overview of Timer control registers per PIC =

<br>Multi-bit fields which take the whole register are not enumerated.
Multi-bit fields smaller than 8 bits are enumerated,
like in the datasheets.
In the device files multi-bit fields are
declared as single variable!

<i>This wiki may be extended later after more analysis.</i>
